Name: ColumnNumber
Description: Column in which data item is found. This is an integer defined in relationship to a specified "first" column NOT the column identifier found in the spreadsheet. Begin numbering columns from the upper left corner of the table as defined in TopLeftTableAnchor attribute "column".

Name: RowSequence
Description: A single case may be represented on a single row or a series of rows, particularly when multiple measures are used. This element designates the row, with the assumption that there is a single row per case unless otherwise stated.
